      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "**Key functional groups / motifs**\n- **One phenyl ring** (anisole-like aryl ether): `c1ccc(... )cc1`\n- **Aryl ether (propoxy substituent):** `CCCO\u2013Ar` (adds lipophilicity)\n- **Thioether linker:** `Ar\u2013CH2\u2013S\u2013` (neutral, polarizable; can increase binding to hydrophobic pockets)\n- **Diacid (malic/succinic-acid-like):** `\u2013CH(\u2013CO2H)\u2013CO2H` (two **carboxylic acids**, strongly acidic)",
      "tool_name": null,
