      "step_index": 3,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "**Structural alerts relevant to CYP2D6 inhibition**\n- Lacks the classic **CYP2D6 inhibitor pharmacophore**: a **basic center** (often tertiary amine) positioned near an aromatic/hydrophobic region.",
      "tool_name": null,
      "tool_input": null,
      "tool_output": null,
